  "about.terms": "Terms of Service",
  "about.intro1": "xcorso is a tool for orienteering course planning. It aims to make course setting more approachable and enjoyable.",
  "about.intro2": "To achieve that, it is or aims to be intuitive, multi-platform, mobile-ready, free, and open source. Compared to other course planning tools, it is definitely not as feature-rich, but it should cover the most common orienteering events.",
  "about.intro3": "It can be used locally without sharing any data, or users can sign in to sync projects across devices.",
