  "about.miss.more": "Many more!",
  "about.feedback": "If you wish to suggest a feature or report a bug, you can do so by opening an issue on <gh>GitHub</gh> or emailing me. Don't forget that the project is open source, so you can also contribute directly! I would warmly welcome any development.",
  "about.contact": "I would love to hear from you no matter what — drop me a line at <email>mmg@xcorso.it</email>.",
  "about.credits": "Finally, there is one library that made this entire project possible: <ocad>ocad2geojson</ocad>.",
  "about.privacy2": "I have tried to respect your privacy as much as possible. If you do not want to use the sync feature, we only collect anonymized error data through Sentry. If you choose to login and sync, the only personal information we store is your email (but your courses will be uploaded). See the <terms>Terms of Service</terms> for a more complete picture.",
  "about.source": "Find the source code for xcorso at <gh>github.com/mmguar/xcorso</gh>. It is distributed under the AGPL 3.0 license.",
  "about.tryDemo": "I'd love it if you took a look at our <demo>demo project</demo> — no account needed.",
